&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;5)&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;Make “Touch of Innoruuk” and all Shadow Knight Life Taps land more frequently.&amp;nbsp; Also make the spell Blood of Inruku land more frequently in pvp and perhaps an adjustment to the spell Dread Gaze.&amp;nbsp; Currently if cast it will aggro any pets etc at the raid.&amp;nbsp; Would it be possible to make it so that it doesn't affect members of a raid's pets? &lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;6)&amp;nbsp; Currently rangers are able to shoot arrows at targets with no need for a line of sight.&amp;nbsp; They shoot arrows on the run at people behind them etc, effectively bow kiting people.&amp;nbsp; Please implement a line of sight requirement for archery.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;No development feedback at this time&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
