&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;7)&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;Increase the ability to resist the Bard mana drain songs currently it is irresistible .&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Also increase the ability to stop bard's selos via some change that allows for it to be stopped when someone hits them/stuns them.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;8)&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please consider running the Discord server again.&amp;nbsp; Many people have requested it and enjoyed it when it was ran as a special event.&amp;nbsp; &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;No development feedback at this time&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;9)&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;Adjust the pvp resists on the monk epic effect, Peace of the Disciple as well as on the DON nuke Dragon Fang.&amp;nbsp; Currently they are for the most part unresistable and it is fairly unbalancing in pvp.&amp;nbsp; &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0066ff&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;10)&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Adjust the resist rates of spells for casters in general.&amp;nbsp; Currently, melee classes have a distinct advantage pvp wise versus casters.&amp;nbsp; With the addition of potions and higher resists etc,&amp;nbsp;casters are rendered fairly disabled in pvp.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; If the resist rates can not be adjusted, consider raising the spell damage cap so that casters are capable of doing more damage in pvp. &lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0066ff&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
