&lt;DIV&gt;6)&amp;nbsp; Currently rangers are able to shoot arrows at targets with no need for a line of sight.&amp;nbsp; They shoot arrows on the run at people behind them etc, effectively bow kiting people.&amp;nbsp; Please implement a line of sight requirement for archery.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0066ff&gt;NEW&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
